meta.title: Ariel: Trapped in the Void - NathanTDA's Video

ttsdata.text: oh my gosh, no one else is here! but me
i think i am trapped in the void
something weird must be going on in whatever this place is, today
hey what just happened to my clothes? and my shoes? and my special skirt?
well, i'm glad i'm still alive after the shutdown of the legacy video maker, and now in the new one
